headline: Goldman Sachs turns bullish on select asset managers, upgrades BEN, AMG
summary: Investing.com -- Goldman Sachs has turned bullish on select traditional asset managers, upgrading Franklin Resources (NYSE:BEN) and Affiliated Managers Group (NYSE:AMG) to Buy, citing improving organic growth prospects and compelling valuations.
